<hr>

Some connections to projects outside of the Labs that I am
affiliated with:
DOS Prevention (<a href="http://seclab.uiuc.edu/contessans/">ContessaNS</a>),
<a href="http://www.cis.upenn.edu/~bcpierce/harmony">Harmony</a>,
<a href="http://www.cis.upenn.edu/~anagnost/cing/">cing</a> (Network Tomography/Measurement),
GK (Summarizing large sets of streaming data),
AHBHA (pronounced "Abba") (Adaptive Hop-by-hop Aggregate congestion control),
<br>
(This list is almost always incomplete).<br>
Some tabled projects:<br>
Canon (consistent security in heterogeneous distributed systems),
<a href="http://www.cis.upenn.edu/~dsl/POSSE/"> POSSE</a>,
TRANSMIT,
<a href="http://www.cis.upenn.edu/~dsl/STRONGMAN/"> Strongman</a>,
ABIDE<br>
